To compile an term given an rider (dereference - in place):
  If the term's variable is nil, abort with "Internal error - compile an term given an rider (dereference - in place)" and the rider; exit.
  Put the term's type's target type's name into the term's type name.
  Put the term's type's target type into the term's type.
  Add an fragment given the dereference tag and the term's variable.
  Clear the term's phrase.
  
  